description.en: It's an erc20 token built on ethereum blockchain with the purpose of stablizing iShop Token (IST) price on the exchanges. Members of the community and external investors can purchase ISP with IST. Also ISP is a peer to peer currency, which can also be used to Shop on iShop portal-https://i-shop.com.ng. ISP has a total supply of 1500000  and 800,000 as circulating supply, which makes the currency relatively scarce. ISP will bridge the gap in the online payment and cross boarder payment.
